1.change value accordingly

		C:\wamp\bin\apache\apache2.2.6\bin\php.ini 
			post_max_size = 750M
			upload_max_filesize = 750M
			max_execution_time = 5000
			max_input_time = 5000
			memory_limit = 1000M 

		C:\wamp\bin\mysql\mysql5.0.45\my.ini:
			max_allowed_packet = 200M 


2.send mail function to be changed accorndingly in php.ini file
		[mail function]

			SMTP = localhost
			smtp_port = 25
			sendmail_from = //Your mail id
			sendmail_path ="C:\wamp\sendmail\sendmail.exe -t -i"


3.file path C:\wamp\sendmail\sendmail.ini file will be changed to

		smtp_server=smtp.gmail.com
		smtp_port=465
		smtp_ssl=ssl
		default_domain=localhost
		error_logfile=error.log
		auth_username=//your mail id 
		auth_password=//your mail id password
		force_sender=//your mail id
		hostname=localhost

